"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa/","name":"What is a Highly Skilled Manpower Visa in Turkey?","datePublished":"2026-03-21T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-22T15:25:14+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"What is a Highly Skilled Manpower Visa in Turkey?","keywords":"Skilled Manpower Visa","datePublished":"2026-03-21T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-22T15:25:14+03:00","articleSection":"Visa and Immigration","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Evaluate work opportunities in Turkey with a highly qualified workforce visa. Learn about the application criteria and the advantages it offers now!","name":"What is a Highly Skilled Manpower Visa in Turkey?","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ''Segoe UI'', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, ''Helvetica Neue'', sans-serif;">Purpose and Importance of the Visa</span></p>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">The highly skilled manpower visa is part of Turkey&#8217;s strategy to attract an international skilled workforce. With this visa, Turkey wants to employ individuals specialized in various fields such as scientists, engineers, and managers. With its developing economic structure, Turkey aims to be competitive in the international arena. Bringing highly qualified manpower to the country will bring technological and scientific developments as well as economic growth.</span><span style="color: #000000;">This visa will raise the standard in a specific area of the Turkish labor market and provide internationally recognized work experience. The value that highly qualified experts will bring to Turkey includes innovative perspectives and the establishment of international standards. This will help Turkey&#8217;s emerging markets become more competitive.</span></div>
<div id="h-who can apply for a high-skilled-human-power-visa" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Who Can Apply for a Highly Skilled Manpower Visa?</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">It is important to meet certain criteria to apply for a highly skilled manpower visa. First of all, you usually need to have a university degree for this visa. Individuals who have received education in fields such as engineering, health, informatics and technology are more likely to benefit from this visa. For example, people with high-level technical knowledge, such as doctors, engineers or IT specialists, are more likely to benefit from this visa.</span><span style="color: #000000;">At the same time, having the necessary professional qualification documents will support your visa applications. This includes not only academic qualifications but also internationally recognized certificates. In this period when Turkey needs a highly qualified workforce, applications from professionals with experience in related fields will be prioritized.</span></div>
<div id="h-high-qualified-human-power-visa-criteria" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Criteria for Highly Skilled Manpower Visa</span></h2>
</div>
<div id="h-egitim-and-professional-competence" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Training and Vocational Qualification</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Candidates applying for a highly skilled manpower visa must first have completed certain levels of academic study. A university degree or higher is the most basic requirement of the application process. At this stage, expertise in fields such as engineering, health, science and informatics provides a significant advantage in visa applications. Therefore, those who have been trained in these fields have a better chance of applying.</span><span style="color: #000000;">However, factors such as professional competence should also be taken into account. Internationally recognized certificates or certificates of expertise are particularly advantageous for those who can prove their professional experience. For example, an internationally recognized engineering certificate held by a professional in the engineering field can strengthen his/her application. </span></div>
<div id="h-istihdam-ve-is-teklifi" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Employment and Job Offer</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Another important criterion for a highly qualified manpower visa is a concrete job offer or employment contract from an employer in Turkey. This is not only necessary for the validity of the visa applied for, but also shows that the applicant will work in a position that is compatible with the competencies that the applicant possesses. The employer must prove that you meet the qualifications required by the position. <span style="color: #000000;">For example, if a prospective engineer wants to work as a software engineer in a technology company in Turkey, he/she should keep in mind that he/she must have a job offer that is suitable for this position. This creates a mutual responsibility for both the employee and the employer and allows the visa process to proceed correctly.</span></span></div>
<div id="h-high-qualified-human-power-visa-basvuru-sureci" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Highly Skilled Manpower Visa Application Process</span></h2>
</div>
<div id="h-basvuru-merkezleri" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Application Centers</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Applications for the highly qualified manpower visa are made at the foreign representations of the Republic of Turkey or at the relevant units of the Directorate General of Migration Management. These institutions are responsible for accepting and evaluating applications. At the time of application, it is important that candidates submit the required documents in full.</span><span style="color: #000000;">In the first stage of the application process, applicants must carefully fill out the visa application form and prepare the required documents. After reviewing your documents, application centers may request additional information or documents if necessary. It is therefore important to stay in touch throughout the entire process. </span></div>
<div id="h-gnecli-belgelerin-hazirlanmasi" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Preparation of Necessary Documents</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">The application process begins with the preparation of the right documents. Documents such as a valid passport, employment contract or job offer, professional and academic qualification documents, visa application form, criminal record and medical certificate are usually required. In addition, a statement of financial situation may be requested. Other supporting documents that may vary depending on the occupational group and position applied for should also be considered.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Complete and accurate preparation of documents is a decisive factor in the acceptance process. Therefore, it is of utmost importance for candidates to ensure that the required documents are complete prior to application. For example, including at least one letter of reference among the prepared documents can be beneficial in terms of supporting professional background.</span></div>
<div id="h-yukseksek-nitelikli-insan-gucu-visa-advantages" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Advantages of Highly Skilled Manpower Visa</span></h2>
</div>
<div id="h-long-sureli-ve-kolaylastirilmis-ikamet-hakki" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Long-term and Facilitated Residence Rights</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">The highly skilled manpower visa, if successfully obtained, entitles the visa holder to long-term residence and work in Turkey. This makes it easier for qualified individuals to find a place in Turkey&#8217;s thriving labor market in the first place. Moreover, the process of renewal and extension of residence and work permits has been greatly simplified, so that professionals can continue their careers in Turkey for the long term.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Acquiring a highly skilled labor visa opens up significant opportunities in business. This is because visa processing is usually completed quickly and going through the necessary application process is very streamlined. In addition, having <a style="color: #000000;" href="https://www.goc.gov.tr/ikamet-izni-cesitleri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">long-term residency</a> rights offers professionals a great advantage when building a career in Turkey.</span></div>
<div id="h-aile-birlestimi- kolayayligi" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Family Reunification Made Easy</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Another advantage for highly skilled manpower visa holders is the ease of family reunification. The visa applicant&#8217;s spouse and children under the age of 18 can enter and reside in Turkey with the visa. This allows a highly skilled workforce to not only enhance their own career prospects, but also maintain family integrity.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Family reunification is an extremely important aspect for individuals who wish to be with their loved ones while living abroad. This advantage also makes it more attractive for potential candidates to start a new life in Turkey. These benefits for highly qualified individuals and their families make Turkey an attractive destination for both professional and personal life.</span></div>
<div id="h-sikca-sorulan-sorular" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Frequently Asked Questions</span></h2>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Who can apply for a highly skilled manpower visa?</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Foreigners with an academic degree, professional competence or a high level of professional experience can apply.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">What documents are required for visa application? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Passport, employment contract, diplomas, professional qualification certificates, medical report, criminal record and application form are required.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">How to get professional qualification equivalence? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">International diplomas can be recognized through equivalency certificates issued by the relevant institutions.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">How long does it take to apply? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">5 to 12 weeks, depending on the volume of applications and completeness of documents.</span></div>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-03-21T11:00:00Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-22T12:25:14Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa';
