</div>
<div id="h-basvuru-merkezleri" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Application Centers</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Applications for the highly qualified manpower visa are made at the foreign representations of the Republic of Turkey or at the relevant units of the Directorate General of Migration Management. These institutions are responsible for accepting and evaluating applications. At the time of application, it is important that candidates submit the required documents in full.</span><span style="color: #000000;">In the first stage of the application process, applicants must carefully fill out the visa application form and prepare the required documents. After reviewing your documents, application centers may request additional information or documents if necessary. It is therefore important to stay in touch throughout the entire process. </span></div>
