<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Preparation of Necessary Documents</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">The application process begins with the preparation of the right documents. Documents such as a valid passport, employment contract or job offer, professional and academic qualification documents, visa application form, criminal record and medical certificate are usually required. In addition, a statement of financial situation may be requested. Other supporting documents that may vary depending on the occupational group and position applied for should also be considered.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Complete and accurate preparation of documents is a decisive factor in the acceptance process. Therefore, it is of utmost importance for candidates to ensure that the required documents are complete prior to application. For example, including at least one letter of reference among the prepared documents can be beneficial in terms of supporting professional background.</span></div>
<div id="h-yukseksek-nitelikli-insan-gucu-visa-advantages" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Advantages of Highly Skilled Manpower Visa</span></h2>
</div>
<div id="h-long-sureli-ve-kolaylastirilmis-ikamet-hakki" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Long-term and Facilitated Residence Rights</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">The highly skilled manpower visa, if successfully obtained, entitles the visa holder to long-term residence and work in Turkey. This makes it easier for qualified individuals to find a place in Turkey&#8217;s thriving labor market in the first place. Moreover, the process of renewal and extension of residence and work permits has been greatly simplified, so that professionals can continue their careers in Turkey for the long term.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Acquiring a highly skilled labor visa opens up significant opportunities in business. This is because visa processing is usually completed quickly and going through the necessary application process is very streamlined. In addition, having <a style="color: #000000;" href="https://www.goc.gov.tr/ikamet-izni-cesitleri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">long-term residency</a> rights offers professionals a great advantage when building a career in Turkey.</span></div>
<div id="h-aile-birlestimi- kolayayligi" class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Family Reunification Made Easy</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Another advantage for highly skilled manpower visa holders is the ease of family reunification. The visa applicant&#8217;s spouse and children under the age of 18 can enter and reside in Turkey with the visa. This allows a highly skilled workforce to not only enhance their own career prospects, but also maintain family integrity.</span><span style="color: #000000;">Family reunification is an extremely important aspect for individuals who wish to be with their loved ones while living abroad. This advantage also makes it more attractive for potential candidates to start a new life in Turkey. These benefits for highly qualified individuals and their families make Turkey an attractive destination for both professional and personal life.</span></div>
<div id="h-sikca-sorulan-sorular" class="wp-block-heading">
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Frequently Asked Questions</span></h2>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Who can apply for a highly skilled manpower visa?</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Foreigners with an academic degree, professional competence or a high level of professional experience can apply.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">What documents are required for visa application? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">Passport, employment contract, diplomas, professional qualification certificates, medical report, criminal record and application form are required.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">How to get professional qualification equivalence? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">International diplomas can be recognized through equivalency certificates issued by the relevant institutions.</span></div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h3><span style="color: #000000;">How long does it take to apply? </span></h3>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph"><span style="color: #000000;">5 to 12 weeks, depending on the volume of applications and completeness of documents.</span></div>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-03-21T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-22T12:25:14Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'what-is-a-highly-skilled-manpower-visa' );
