<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Residence permits are mandatory for international students who will be staying in Turkey for&nbsp;<a href="https://www.goc.gov.tr/ikamet-izni-cesitleri" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">long-term</a>. You should prepare the following documents for the application process:</p>



