<li>4 biometric photographs</li>



<li>Health insurance</li>



<li>Study residence permit application form</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more details, see&nbsp;<a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/long-term-residence-permit/">Residence Permit in Turkey: Guide for International Students</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-process-and-renewal">Application Process and Renewal</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Residence permits are usually issued for one year and can be renewed throughout the study period. You can complete the procedures more easily by getting support from your university’s student affairs office.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="housing-options-and-layout">Housing Options and Layout</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="hostels-a-safe-and-social-option">Hostels: A Safe and Social Option</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Public and private dormitories offer advantages in terms of security, food service and social activities. Dormitories are a good starting point for students who want to build a social network in a new city. However, it is recommended to book early to avoid a shortage of space.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="share-houses-and-residences">Share Houses and Residences</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Shared homes offer a freer lifestyle and can often be a more affordable solution. When looking for a house, consider location, safety and rental costs. Student residences are comfortable but more costly alternatives.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="school-shuttle-and-transportation-rules">School Shuttle and Transportation Rules</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-shuttle-rules">Student Shuttle Rules</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many schools in big cities have student shuttles. Shuttles are obliged to deliver students to school at least 15 minutes before class. In case of a change of address, be sure to contact the service company and the school administration.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="security-and-remuneration">Security and Remuneration</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Services must be staffed by a guide. It is important not to go off-route and not to exceed the transport limit. Pricing varies depending on distance; it may be worth checking if there are discounts for paying in advance.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="official-and-daily-life-transactions">Official and Daily Life Transactions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="address-registration-and-residency-process">Address Registration and Residency Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Within 30 days of entering Turkey, you must register your address with the Population Directorate. This procedure allows you to stay in Turkey legally and prevents any official problems that may arise in the future.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="bank-and-transportation-card">Bank and Transportation Card</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To survive in Turkey, you will need to open a local bank account. You can also make your daily life easier by issuing a student card and a city public transportation card (e.g. Istanbulkart or Ankarakart).</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="complete-your-moving-process-successfully">Complete Your Moving Process Successfully!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Moving to Turkey for education can be made easier with good preparation and the right steps. From moving to residence permits, accommodation, transportation and official procedures, you can start your new life with confidence. Remember, your academic success in Turkey is directly related to how well you adapt to this transition.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-rights-are-granted-with-a-student-residence-permit-in-turkey">What rights are granted with a student residence permit in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to the student residence permit, international students can legally reside in Turkey, study at the universities they are enrolled in and carry out legal procedures such as compulsory health insurance. It also offers benefits such as access to social services and student discounts.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-pay-the-most-attention-to-when-moving">What to pay the most attention to when moving</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The most common mistake made during the moving process is to act unprepared and with hasty decisions. Staying to the last minute, especially in choosing a transportation company, can both increase costs and cause damage to the goods. Early planning, choosing insured transportation and the official address notification process are the main issues that should be prioritized.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What are the advantages of moving by private service?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Private transportation companies facilitate the process by offering special services for students. A transportation plan customized according to personal needs ensures safer transportation of goods. In addition, delivery tracking and customer support means that any problems can be resolved more quickly. This makes the process both safer and more stress-free.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-03-19T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-20T21:58:02Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'moving-guide-for-long-term-students-in-turkey' );
