ressing-and-beauty/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/affordable-hairdressing-and-beauty/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/affordable-hairdressing-and-beauty-services-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/affordable-hairdressing-and-beauty/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Finding budget-friendly hairdressing and beauty services for students is important for international students studying in Turkey. Many hairdressers and beauty salons in Turkey offer special discounts for students. Halls, especially in areas close to university campuses, serve students at affordable prices.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-discounts">Student Discounts</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Hair Salons:</strong> Many hair salons offer discounts of 10% to 20% to students. Services such as haircuts, color changes and styling can be obtained at more affordable prices when showing a student ID.</li>



<li><strong>Beauty Salons:</strong> There are similar discounts for services such as skin care, manicure and pedicure. Some salons organize special offers for students on certain days.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also benefit from our article on <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/water-saving-bill-management-in-turkey/">How to Save Money on Bills in Turkey</a>.</p>



