<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="price-comparison-of-hairdresser-and-beauty-services-in-turkey">Price Comparison of Hairdresser and Beauty Services in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Prices for hairdressing and beauty services in Turkey vary from city to city and according to the quality of the salon. In general, prices are higher in big cities, while it is possible to find more affordable prices in smaller cities.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="price-ranges">Price Ranges</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong data-start="264" data-end="279">Haircut:</strong><br>20-30 USD in big cities, 10-15 USD in small cities</li>



<li><strong data-start="339" data-end="373">Hair coloring (bleaching + dyeing):</strong><br>40-70 USD in big cities, 25-40 USD in small cities</li>



<li><strong data-start="434" data-end="465">Skin care (classic care):</strong><br>USD 25-40 in big cities, USD 15-25 in small cities</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These prices may vary depending on the location of the hall and the quality of services it offers. It is important for students to consider options that fit their budget.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also check out <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/seasonal-clothing-shopping-tips-in-turkey/" data-type="link" data-id="https://roadtostudy.com/en/seasonal-clothing-shopping-tips-in-turkey/">Tips for Seasonal Clothes Shopping in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="beauty-trends-and-recommendations-in-turkey-for-international-students">Beauty Trends and Recommendations in Turkey for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Beauty trends in Turkey are progressing in parallel with developments around the world. Students can keep themselves up to date by following these trends.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="current-beauty-trends">Current Beauty Trends</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Natural Beauty:</strong> Recently, interest in natural and organic products has increased. Students prefer natural products for skin care.</li>



<li><strong>Minimalist Makeup:</strong> Light and natural makeup styles have become popular, especially among young people.</li>



<li><strong>Naturalness in Hair Care:</strong> Natural oils and masks are used in hair care.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="suggestions">Suggestions</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Discover Local Salons:</strong> By discovering local hair and beauty salons, you can find affordable and quality services.</li>



<li><strong>Follow Campaigns:</strong> You can save your budget by following the campaigns and discounts organized by the salons.</li>



