<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-discounts">Student Discounts</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Hair Salons:</strong> Many hair salons offer discounts of 10% to 20% to students. Services such as haircuts, color changes and styling can be obtained at more affordable prices when showing a student ID.</li>



<li><strong>Beauty Salons:</strong> There are similar discounts for services such as skin care, manicure and pedicure. Some salons organize special offers for students on certain days.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also benefit from our article on <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/water-saving-bill-management-in-turkey/">How to Save Money on Bills in Turkey</a>.</p>



