<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Online shopping offers advantages such as convenience, variety and frequent discounts.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-cultural-differences-affect-clothes-shopping">How cultural differences affect clothes shopping</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is possible to find modern and diverse clothes in big cities, while in smaller cities more traditional and local clothes are at the forefront.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-01-08T10:48:59Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:39:48Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/seasonal-clothing-shopping-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"People shopping for seasonal clothes in Turkey","title":"seasonal-clothing-shopping-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'seasonal-clothing-shopping-tips-in-turkey' );
