<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-influences-clothing-and-personal-care-habits-in-turkey">Cultural Influences: Clothing and Personal Care Habits in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey, with its rich cultural diversity, also influences clothing and personal care habits. Different regions have different clothing styles and understandings of personal care. For example:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">&#8211; <strong>Traditional Clothing:</strong> In some parts of Turkey, traditional clothing is still used in daily life. Especially in rural areas, local clothes and handmade products are preferred.</p>



