<p class="wp-block-paragraph">&#8211; <strong>Personal Care Concept:</strong> In Turkey, personal care is important not only for aesthetics but also for health. Traditional Turkish bath culture has an important place in skin care and hygiene.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="dont-miss-the-tips-for-affordable-shopping">Don&#8217;t Miss the Tips for Affordable Shopping!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey offers a rich market for clothing and personal care products, meeting the needs of students. Budget-friendly options, seasonal discounts and a shopping experience enriched by cultural influences provide great advantages for students studying in Turkey. It is possible to find both economical and quality products by taking into account the points to be considered while shopping. Shopping for clothing and personal care in Turkey not only fulfills needs, but also enriches students&#8217; social lives by providing a cultural experience.</p>



