<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Requesting these documents will increase your security during the rental process.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="find-the-right-house-with-the-right-source">Find the Right House with the Right Source!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When looking for a house to rent in Turkey, using reliable sources and platforms helps the process go more smoothly. Determining your budget, evaluating the location and checking reliability will help you find the right home. Remember, always be careful and seek professional help when needed. We wish you success in your rental house search!</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-how-much-are-the-rental-prices-in-turkey">1. How much are the rental prices in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Home prices for rent vary from city to city. In big cities like Istanbul, prices are usually higher, starting at USD 100 and going up to USD 1250.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-which-documents-should-i-request-when-looking-for-a-house-to-rent">2. Which documents should I request when looking for a house to rent?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You should request documents such as the landlord&#8217;s identity document, title deed, lease agreement and a copy of the last invoice.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-what-should-i-pay-attention-to-when-looking-for-a-house-to-rent">3. What should I pay attention to when looking for a house to rent?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You should pay attention to factors such as budget, location, housing situation, security and contract terms.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-what-are-the-trusted-rental-platforms">4. What are the trusted rental platforms?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Platforms such as Sahibinden.com, Hürriyet Emlak, Zingat, Emlakjet can help you find reliable rental houses.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-how-to-conduct-local-market-research">5. How to conduct local market research?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Internet research, contacting local real estate agents, gathering information through social media and forums are effective methods of local market research.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-14T10:16:09Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:46:29Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/reliable-resources-when-looking-for-a-house-to-rent-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Reliable Sources When Looking for a House to Rent in Turkey","title":"reliable-resources-when-looking-for-a-house-to-rent-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'reliable-resources-for-renting-a-house-in-turkey' );
