<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, national holidays and celebrations are not only history, but also cultural experiences. Celebrating these special days can make your study life in Turkey more meaningful.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-12-22T21:39:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:48:15Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/guide-to-national-holidays-and-celebrations-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Anıtkabir with red and white balloons at sunset.","title":"guide-to-national-holidays-and-celebrations-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'national-holidays-in-turkey' );
