<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Galatasaray, Fenerbahçe and Beşiktaş are the most popular football clubs in Turkey.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-sport-events-are-organized-in-turkey">Which sport events are organized in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports events such as the Istanbul Marathon, Bodrum Cup and the Turkish Open Tennis Tournament are organized.</p>



